Cannes 2025 Full Recap Newsletter: https://www.seeingthroughfilm.com/p/eddingtons-americana-lunacy-cannes Part II:
Watch @LikeStoriesofOld Cannes Recap: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wTpWVm9sZ2U
Chapters: 00:00 One of The Best Film of The Year 01:06 Cannes Film Festival 02:51 Chapter I: Victims of High Expectations 03:12 Eddington Review 05:30 Honorable Mentions 06:19 Urchin (UK) 07:09 The Chronology of Water (US) 07:53 The Love That Remains (Iceland) 09:06 Resurrection (China) 10:49 Splitsville (US) 12:12 Two Prosecutors (Ukraine) 13:02 Best of Cannes 13:12 2000 Meters To Andriivka (Ukraine) 14:42 Nouvelle Vague (US) 16:32 The Sound of Falling (Germany) 19:00 My Father's Shadow (Nigeria) 19:57 It Was Just An Accident (Iran) 22:38 Sirat (Spain) 25:02 Sentimental Value (Norway) 26:01 Au Revoir
Corrections: 19:29 My Father's Shadow was not the first Nigerian film at Cannes but the first film to premiere at Cannes In Competition
